Tidak, Pak.

65
00:05:03,490 --> 00:05:04,491
Aku paham.

66
00:05:26,555 --> 00:05:27,555
Hei.

67
00:05:31,601 --> 00:05:33,603
Sial, kau minum-minum?

68
00:05:36,690 --> 00:05:38,025
Kenapa tak bisa menembak?

69
00:05:43,905 --> 00:05:44,948
Maafkan aku.

70
00:05:47,117 --> 00:05:48,160
Hei.

71
00:05:48,994 --> 00:05:51,038
Tak apa. Kau sudah bagus.

72
00:05:54,166 --> 00:05:58,754
Namun, kupastikan saja.

73
00:05:58,837 --> 00:06:01,423
Kau tak akan lapor polisi

74
00:06:01,506 --> 00:06:03,675
